
Simple hotel management system with data from Mysql database.

1) Improvements ideas:

1) optimalization database data,
2) gui interface or web based interface,
3) changing or improve project structure,
4) better input data errors handling,
5) extra user data functionality:
- remove user by id,
- editing user data,
- generating charts,
- and more?

All ideas came from 10 minutes redesigning thinking about project at all.
In time ideas will be improved.


2) What direction will be taken for this project?

This project was created as simple as possible project for training python
with database management data.

Version 1.0 is basic version which can or can't be improved.
